            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[### What's new
- **Command blocks** — Kommando now marks each command you run. Click one to select it, use ⌥↑ / ⌥↓ to cycle between commands, ⌘C to copy the whole block, or right-click for a context menu (copy / paste / clear).

### Fixes
- Microphone and camera now work in terminal programs — child processes correctly inherit the permissions instead of being silently denied (#4).
]]></description>
